{"id":3296,"date":"2021-12-20T17:28:43","date_gmt":"2021-12-20T10:28:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/?p=3296"},"modified":"2021-12-20T17:28:43","modified_gmt":"2021-12-20T10:28:43","slug":"da-emerald-thien-nhien-la-gi-nhung-dieu-ban-chua-biet-ve-ngoc-luc-bao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/da-emerald-thien-nhien-la-gi-nhung-dieu-ban-chua-biet-ve-ngoc-luc-bao\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110\u00e1 Emerald Thi\u00ean Nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? Nh\u1eefng \u0110i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wDYxhc\" lang=\"vi-VN\" data-attrid=\"ss:\/webfacts:mau\" data-md=\"1001\" data-hveid=\"CDAQAA\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-6uKlh_L0AhUTVPUHHQuKCHgQkCl6BAgwEAA\">\n<div class=\"Z1hOCe\">\n<div class=\"zloOqf PZPZlf\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-6uKlh_L0AhUTVPUHHQuKCHgQyxMoAHoECDAQAQ\">\n<div>\u0110\u00e1 Emerald hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00fd nh\u00f3m 1 ,trong h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1 beryl c\u00f3 m\u00e0u xanh l\u1ee5c r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p<\/div>\n<div><a href=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3297 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-1.jpg\" alt=\"Emerald Thi\u00ean Nhi\u00ean (1)\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-1.jpg 750w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-1-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div><\/div>\n<div><span><span class=\"\">Ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00fd beryl c\u00f3 m\u00e0u xanh l\u1ee5c t\u1eeb trung b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn xanh \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n, trong \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0u xanh l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c\u00a0<\/span><\/span><span><span class=\"\">t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t<\/span><\/span><span><span class=\"\">\u00a0c\u1ee7a crom (Cr), vanadi (V), ho\u1eb7c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai.\u00a0<\/span>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u0103m 1963, \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n\u00a0<\/span><span>Beryll<\/span><span>\u00a0v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t crom, nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf Brazil \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ecdc l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e1 beryl m\u00e0u xanh b\u1edfi vanadi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed5i.\u00a0<span class=\"\">Theo \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9 tinh khi\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e3o h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a m\u00e0u xanh l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a beryl l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o.<\/span><\/span><\/div>\n<div><a href=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Emeral-Tho-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1842 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Emeral-Tho-4.jpg\" alt=\"Emeral Tho 4.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Emeral-Tho-4.jpg 500w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Emeral-Tho-4-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Emeral-Tho-4-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Emeral-Tho-4-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/a><\/div>\n<div class=\"rVusze\">\n<table class=\"infobox\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">M\u00e0u<\/th>\n<td>Th\u1ee7y tinh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">D\u1ea1ng th\u01b0\u1eddng tinh th\u1ec3<\/th>\n<td>C\u00e1c tinh th\u1ec3 l\u1ee5c gi\u00e1c<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">C\u00e1t khai<\/th>\n<td>C\u00e1t khai \u0111\u00e1y k\u00e9m<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">V\u1ebft v\u1ee1<\/th>\n<td>V\u1ecf s\u00f2 (concoit)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">\u0110\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng Mohs<\/th>\n<td>7,5-8,0<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">\u00c1nh<\/th>\n<td>Th\u1ee7y tinh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">M\u00e0u v\u1ebft v\u1ea1ch<\/th>\n<td>tr\u1eafng<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">T\u1ef7 tr\u1ecdng ri\u00eang<\/th>\n<td>2,7-2,78<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">Chi\u1ebft su\u1ea5t<\/th>\n<td>~1,576-1,582<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">\u0110a s\u1eafc<\/th>\n<td>L\u1ee5c-lam, l\u1ee5c-v\u00e0ng<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope=\"row\">Nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00f3ng ch\u1ea3y<\/th>\n<td>1.278\u00a0\u00b0C<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Gi\u00e1 Emerald<\/h2>\n<p>Ngay c\u1ea3 khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00fd kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft ti\u1ec1n, ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u cao tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.\u00a0Gi\u00e1 Panna b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb\u00a0<strong>\u20b9 800 (12,30 USD) v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi \u20b9 2 lakh (3076 USD) cho m\u1ed7i carat<\/strong>\u00a0, t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9 trong, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00fd.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3298 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-2.jpg\" alt=\"Emerald Thi\u00ean Nhi\u00ean (2)\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-2.jpg 750w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-2-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-2-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Emerald-Thien-Nhien-2-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<ul class=\"bullet\">\n<li>\n<h3>Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c<\/h3>\n<p>Nh\u1edd ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, ph\u1ea1m vi gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o Colombia \u1edf \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u00f3\u00a0<strong>gi\u00e1<\/strong> t\u1eeb\u00a0<strong>49,23 \u0111\u00f4 la \u0111\u1ebfn 3076 \u0111\u00f4 la M\u1ef9 m\u1ed9t carat<\/strong>\u00a0.\u00a0Ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o Zambia c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb<strong>41,5 \u0111\u1ebfn 2307,69 USD m\u1ed9t carat<\/strong>\u00a0.\u00a0Ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o Brazil c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1c m\u1ecf Panna \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf Colombia, Zambia, Brazil, Nga, Pakistan, Afghanistan, Hoa K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 Australia.\u00a0C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e3o h\u00f2a cao v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c s\u1eafc xanh l\u1ee5c v\u00e0 xanh lam,\u00a0<strong>ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o Colombia<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 cao c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c, ti\u1ebfp theo l\u00e0 ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o Zambia.\u00a0Ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o Brazil c\u00f3 m\u00e0u t\u1ed1i v\u00e0 do \u0111\u00f3 \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<li>\n<h3>M\u00e0u s\u1eafc<\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o, quy t\u1eafc m\u00e0u c\u00e0ng s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u00e0ng xanh th\u00ec gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e0ng cao.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean, qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1eaft (\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra m\u00e0u h\u01a1i xanh v\u00e0 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m\u00a0<strong>gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00fd Ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o xanh tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/strong>\u00a0.\u00a0V\u00ec ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o t\u1eeb Colombia c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e3o h\u00f2a sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t gi\u1eefa m\u00e0u xanh l\u00e1 c\u00e2y v\u00e0 xanh lam,\u00a0<strong>gi\u00e1 m\u1ed7i carat ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o Colombia<\/strong>\u00a0v\u1eabn cao h\u01a1n c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c.<\/li>\n<li>\n<h3>\u0110\u1ed9 trong<\/h3>\n<p>Ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 &#8216;Lo\u1ea1i III&#8217; d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 trong, ng\u1ee5 \u00fd r\u1eb1ng h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft m\u1ecdi m\u1ea3nh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t.\u00a0Do \u0111\u00f3, chi ph\u00ed panna t\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u00a0<strong>Gi\u00e1 m\u1ed7i carat ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o Zambia<\/strong> cao h\u01a1n c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c do \u0111\u1ed9 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u00e1 Emerald hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00fd nh\u00f3m 1 ,trong h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1 beryl c\u00f3 m\u00e0u xanh l\u1ee5c r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p Ng\u1ecdc l\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00fd beryl c\u00f3 m\u00e0u xanh l\u1ee5c t\u1eeb trung b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn xanh \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n, trong \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0u xanh l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c\u00a0t\u1ea1p &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3298,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[176],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3296"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3296"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3296\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3299,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3296\/revisions\/3299"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3298"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3296"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3296"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/daquyphongthuyPTJ.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3296"}],"curies":[{"nam